      <h1>Departments</h1> 
      <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
       <div class="pageDescription"><p>The Ministry of Labour has&nbsp;six departments. <br />The Press and Communications Division is part of the Secretary General’s staff.</p> </div>       
    </div>
    
               
        
    
