            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/aid/about-the-ministry/organization/departments/the-department-of-welfare-policy.html?id=1456" title="">
                    The Department of Welfare Policy
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                The Department of Welfare Policy is responsible for policies aimed at assuring income through sickness benefit, rehabilitation benefits, time-limited disability benefits and disability pensions in the national insurance scheme, and through social security assistance.
