                <a href="/en/dep/aid/about-the-ministry/organization/departments/the-department-of-finance.html?id=973" title="">
                    The Department of Finance
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                The Department is responsible for coordinating, quality assuring and providing guidance in connection with the Ministry’s work relating to its budget and finances.

            </p>
